rows.label: tev071401_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Kun'luarb if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0001
rows.name:
So long as you are willing to protect us, you are free
to use the technologies we provide however you wish.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0002
rows.name:
It is no concern of ours if, like the Ganglion,
you employ them to oppress other xenoforms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Though needless to say, that course of action would
endanger humanity by turning other xenoforms against
you and decreasing the odds of your survival.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0004
rows.name:
So I consider it unlikely that you would pursue so
foolish a course. That is why we have calculated your
odds of victory to be as high as 51 percent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0008
rows.name:
Even in the harsh environs of this world,
we Orphe must find a way to progenate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0009
rows.name:
This is an Orphean biological imperative that we
prioritize even higher than our individual survival.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0010
rows.name:
However, we have not yet sensed in this world the
thing we need in order to reproduce.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0011
rows.name:
It is possible this is a result of our Ovah indicating
that the time is not yet right for reproduction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev071401_MSG0012
rows.name:
But when that time does come, I hope you humans will
honor our alliance and aid us.[ST:wait ]
